  {
    "content_id": 571643,
    "reference_id": 123278,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 1:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17001016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>根據米母干的回答，瓦實提得罪了誰？</strong></p><p>王后瓦實提這事，不但得罪王，並且有害於亞哈隨魯王各省的臣民。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17001016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 1:16",
          "end_ref": "17001016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 1:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571644,
    "reference_id": 123279,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 1:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17001017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>米母干說波斯和米底亞的眾婦人聽見王后這事，會怎麼做？</strong></p><p>米母干說，因為王后這事必傳到眾婦人的耳中，國中的婦人知道王后所做的事後，她們就藐視自己的丈夫，並說：「亞哈隨魯王吩咐他的臣僕帶王后瓦實提到王面前，她卻不來！」</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17001017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 1:17",
          "end_ref": "17001017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 1:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571645,
    "reference_id": 123280,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 1:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17001018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>米母干說那一日，波斯和米底亞的眾夫人會做什麼？</strong></p><p>因為王后這事必傳到眾婦人的耳中，她們就藐視自己的丈夫，當她們說：「亞哈隨魯王吩咐人帶瓦實提王后到他面前，她卻不來。」今日，波斯和米底亞的眾夫人聽見王后這事，必向王的大臣照樣行，從此必大開藐視和忿怒之端。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17001018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 1:18",
          "end_ref": "17001018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 1:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571646,
    "reference_id": 123281,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 1:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17001019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>王會將瓦實提王后的位分賜給誰？</strong></p><p>王會將瓦實提王后的位分賜給比她還好的人。。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17001019",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 1:19",
          "end_ref": "17001019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 1:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571647,
    "reference_id": 123282,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 1:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17001022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>王下了什麼命令？</strong></p><p>王發詔書，使為丈夫的在家中作主，各說本地的方言。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17001022",
