    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571649,
    "reference_id": 123284,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 2:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17002003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>那些處女會被交給誰來照顧？</strong></p><p>那些處女會被交給希該，他是掌管女子的太監。這意味著希該是負責照顧那些處女的人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17002003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 2:3",
          "end_ref": "17002003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 2:3"
