    "reference_id": 123285,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 2:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17002006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>誰從耶路撒冷帶走了基士？</strong></p><p>巴比倫王尼布甲尼撒將基士從耶路撒冷擄去，</p>",
