    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571653,
    "reference_id": 123288,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 2:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17002009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>希該提供了什麼給以斯帖？</strong></p><p>希該急忙給她需用的香品和她所當得的分，又派所當得的七個宮女服事她。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17002009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 2:9",
          "end_ref": "17002009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 2:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571654,
    "reference_id": 123289,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 2:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17002010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以斯帖為什麼未曾將她的籍貫和宗族告訴人？</strong></p><p>以斯帖未曾將籍貫宗族告訴人，因為末底改囑咐她不可叫人知道。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17002010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 2:10",
          "end_ref": "17002010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 2:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571655,
    "reference_id": 123290,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 2:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17002013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>當一個女子進去見王時，要給她什麼？</strong></p><p>凡她所要的都必給她。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17002013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 2:13",
          "end_ref": "17002013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 2:13"
        }
