  },
  {
    "content_id": 571656,
    "reference_id": 123291,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 2:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17002014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>女子什麼時候會再進去見王？</strong></p><p>女子就不再進去見王，除非王喜愛她，再提名召她。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17002014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 2:14",
          "end_ref": "17002014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 2:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571657,
    "reference_id": 123292,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 2:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17002015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以斯帖求了什麼？</strong></p><p>除了掌管女子的太監希該所派定給她的，她別無所求。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17002015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 2:15",
          "end_ref": "17002015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 2:15"
        }
