    "reference_id": 123293,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 2:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17002016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以斯帖是什麼時候被引入宮見亞哈隨魯王的？</strong></p><p>亞哈隨魯王第七年十月（就是提別月），以斯帖被引入宮見亞哈隨魯王。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17002016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 2:16",
          "end_ref": "17002016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 2:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571659,
    "reference_id": 123294,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 2:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17002017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>王為什麼把王后的冠冕戴在以斯帖頭上，並立她為王后？</strong></p><p>王愛以斯帖過於愛眾女，她在王眼前蒙寵愛比眾處女更甚。王就把王后的冠冕戴在她頭上，立她為王后，代替瓦實提。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17002017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 2:17",
          "end_ref": "17002017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 2:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
