    "reference_id": 123295,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 2:21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17002021",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>辟探和提列想要對亞哈隨魯王做什麼事？</strong></p><p>王的太監中有兩個守門的，辟探和提列，惱恨亞哈隨魯王，想要下手害他。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17002021",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 2:21",
          "end_ref": "17002021",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 2:21"
        }
