  {
    "content_id": 571663,
    "reference_id": 123298,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 3:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17003004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>末底改拒絕做什麼？</strong></p><p>末底改不跪不拜。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17003004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 3:4",
          "end_ref": "17003004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 3:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571664,
    "reference_id": 123299,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 3:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17003006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>哈曼想要殺誰？</strong></p><p>哈曼想要滅絕亞哈隨魯王通國所有的猶大人，就是末底改的本族。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17003006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 3:6",
          "end_ref": "17003006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 3:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571665,
    "reference_id": 123300,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 3:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17003008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>當他們掣籤時，擇定了哪一個月？</strong></p><p>亞哈隨魯王十二年正月，就是尼散月，人在哈曼面前，按日日月月掣普珥（即「籤」），要定何月何日為吉，擇定了十二月，就是亞達月。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17003008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 3:8",
          "end_ref": "17003008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 3:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571666,
    "reference_id": 123301,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 3:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17003009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>如果王下令滅絕猶大人，哈曼願意捐多少銀子給王的府庫？</strong></p><p>哈曼說他願意捐一萬他連得銀子交給掌管國帑的人，納入王的府庫。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17003009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 3:9",
          "end_ref": "17003009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 3:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571667,
    "reference_id": 123302,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 3:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17003013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>旨意是如何傳到王的各省的？</strong></p><p>旨意是交給驛卒，傳到王的各省。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17003013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 3:13",
          "end_ref": "17003013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 3:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571668,
    "reference_id": 123303,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 3:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17003015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>書珊城的民對旨意有何回應？</strong></p><p>書珊城的民都慌亂。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17003015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 3:15",
          "end_ref": "17003015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 3:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571669,
    "reference_id": 123304,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 4:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17004002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>末底改走了多遠？為什麼？</strong></p><p>他只到了朝門前就停住腳步，因為穿麻衣的不可進朝門。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17004002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 4:2",
          "end_ref": "17004002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 4:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571670,
    "reference_id": 123305,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 4:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17004004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>當以斯帖送衣服給末底改穿時，他如何回應？</strong></p><p>以斯帖送衣服給末底改穿，要他脫下麻衣，末底改卻不接受。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17004004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 4:4",
          "end_ref": "17004004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 4:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571671,
    "reference_id": 123306,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 4:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17004007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>末底改告訴了哈他革什麼事？</strong></p><p>末底改將自己所遇的事，並哈曼為滅絕猶大人應許捐入王庫的銀數都告訴了他。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17004007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 4:7",
          "end_ref": "17004007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 4:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571672,
    "reference_id": 123307,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 4:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17004008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼末底改將所抄寫傳遍書珊城要滅絕猶大人的旨意，交給哈他革？</strong></p><p>末底改將所抄寫傳遍書珊城要滅絕猶大人的旨意交給哈他革，要給以斯帖看，又要給她說明，並囑咐她進去見王，為本族的人在王面前懇切祈求。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17004008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 4:8",
          "end_ref": "17004008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 4:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571673,
    "reference_id": 123308,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 4:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17004011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>若不蒙召，擅入內院見王的，無論男女，會發生什麼事？</strong></p><p>有一個定例，就是若不蒙召，擅入內院見王的，無論男女必被治死，除非王向他伸出金杖，否則不得存活。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17004011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 4:11",
          "end_ref": "17004011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 4:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571674,
    "reference_id": 123309,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 4:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17004014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>末底改說，此時以斯帖若閉口不言，將會怎樣？</strong></p><p>此時以斯帖若閉口不言，猶大人必從別處得解脫，蒙拯救，以斯帖和她的父家必致滅亡。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17004014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 4:14",
          "end_ref": "17004014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 4:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571675,
    "reference_id": 123310,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 4:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17004016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以斯帖告訴末底改要做什麼？</strong></p><p>以斯帖說，末底改當去招聚書珊城所有的猶大人，為她禁食三晝三夜，不吃不喝，以斯帖和她的宮女也要這樣禁食。然後以斯帖違例進去見王，她若死就死了。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17004016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 4:16",
          "end_ref": "17004016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 4:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571676,
    "reference_id": 123311,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 5:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17005001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>王宮的內院在哪裡？</strong></p><p>王宮的內院正對著王的住宅。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17005001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 5:1",
          "end_ref": "17005001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 5:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571677,
    "reference_id": 123312,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 5:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17005002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>王見王后以斯帖站在院內，為什麼向她伸出手中的金杖？</strong></p><p>王見王后以斯帖站在院內，就施恩於她，向她伸出手中的金杖。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17005002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 5:2",
          "end_ref": "17005002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 5:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571678,
    "reference_id": 123313,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 5:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17005004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以斯帖向王提出了什麼請求？</strong></p><p>以斯帖對王說，王若以為美，就請王帶著哈曼今日赴她所預備的筵席。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17005004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 5:4",
          "end_ref": "17005004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 5:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571679,
    "reference_id": 123314,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 5:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17005008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以斯帖第二次向王提出了什麼請求？</strong></p><p>以斯帖對王說：「我若在王眼前蒙恩，王若願意賜我所要的，准我所求的，就請王帶著哈曼再赴我所要預備的筵席。明日我必照王所問的說明。」 </p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17005008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 5:8",
          "end_ref": "17005008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 5:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571680,
    "reference_id": 123315,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 5:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17005011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>哈曼向他的家人講述了什麼事？</strong></p><p>哈曼將他富厚的榮耀、眾多的兒女，和王抬舉他使他超乎首領臣僕之上，都述說給他們聽。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17005011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 5:11",
          "end_ref": "17005011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 5:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571681,
    "reference_id": 123316,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 5:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17005013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>對哈曼來說，比被邀請赴筵席更重要的事是什麼？</strong></p><p>雖然哈曼有這一切榮耀，但是他看見猶大人末底改坐在朝門，哈曼覺得這榮耀也與他無益。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17005013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 5:13",
          "end_ref": "17005013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 5:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571682,
    "reference_id": 123317,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 5:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17005014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>細利斯告訴哈曼要做什麼？為什麼？</strong></p><p>她要他讓人立一個五丈高的木架，明早求王讓人將末底改掛在其上。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17005014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 5:14",
          "end_ref": "17005014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 5:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571683,
    "reference_id": 123318,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 6:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17006001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼王吩咐人取歷史來，念給他聽？</strong></p><p>那夜王睡不著覺，就吩咐人取歷史來，念給他聽。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17006001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 6:1",
          "end_ref": "17006001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 6:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571684,
    "reference_id": 123319,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 6:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17006002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>在念給王聽的歷史書上寫著什麼事？</strong></p><p>正遇見書上寫著說，王的太監中有兩個守門的，辟探和提列，想要下手害亞哈隨魯王，末底改將這事報告了。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17006002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 6:2",
          "end_ref": "17006002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 6:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571685,
    "reference_id": 123320,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 6:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17006003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>末底改報告了辟探和提列這件事，是否賜他甚麼尊榮爵位？</strong></p><p>對於末底改報告辟探和提列這件事，沒有賜他甚麼尊榮爵位。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17006003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 6:3",
          "end_ref": "17006003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 6:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571686,
    "reference_id": 123321,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 6:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17006006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>當王問哈曼，王所喜悅尊榮的人，當如何待他時，哈曼以為王在說誰？</strong></p><p>哈曼心裏說：「王所喜悅尊榮的，不是我是誰呢？」</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17006006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 6:6",
          "end_ref": "17006006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 6:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571687,
    "reference_id": 123322,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 6:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17006009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>誰會給那位王所喜悅尊榮的人穿上衣服，使他騎上馬，走遍城裏的街市？</strong></p><p>王極尊貴的一個大臣會做這些事情。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17006009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 6:9",
          "end_ref": "17006009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 6:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571688,
    "reference_id": 123323,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 6:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17006011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>是誰將朝服給末底改穿上，使他騎上馬，走遍城裏的街市？</strong></p><p>於是，哈曼拿上朝服和帶上御馬，哈曼將朝服給末底改穿上，使他騎上馬，走遍城裏的街市，在他面前宣告說：「王所喜悅尊榮的人，就如此待他！」</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17006011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 6:11",
          "end_ref": "17006011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 6:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571689,
    "reference_id": 123324,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 6:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17006013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>哈曼的智慧人和他的妻對他警告什麼事？</strong></p><p>哈曼的智慧人和他的妻對他說：「你在末底改面前始而敗落，他如果是猶大人，你必不能勝他，終必在他面前敗落。」</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17006013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 6:13",
          "end_ref": "17006013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 6:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571690,
    "reference_id": 123325,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 7:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17007003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以斯帖向亞哈隨魯王求了什麼？</strong></p><p>以斯帖說：「我所願的，是願王將我的性命賜給我，我所求的，是求王將我的本族賜給我。」</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17007003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 7:3",
          "end_ref": "17007003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 7:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571691,
    "reference_id": 123326,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 7:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17007004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以斯帖說，如果她和她的本族只是被賣為奴為婢，她會怎麼做？</strong></p><p>現在，他們若被賣為奴為婢，她會閉口不言。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17007004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 7:4",
          "end_ref": "17007004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 7:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571692,
    "reference_id": 123327,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 7:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17007006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以斯帖形容誰為「仇人」和「敵人」？</strong></p><p>仇人敵人就是這惡人哈曼！</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17007006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 7:6",
          "end_ref": "17007006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 7:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571693,
    "reference_id": 123328,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 7:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17007007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>當王大怒，起來離開酒席時，哈曼做了什麼事？</strong></p><p>哈曼留下來，求王后以斯帖救他的命。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17007007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 7:7",
          "end_ref": "17007007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 7:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571694,
    "reference_id": 123329,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 7:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17007008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>當哈曼伏在以斯帖所靠的榻上時，王認為哈曼在做什麼？</strong></p><p>王以為哈曼竟敢在宮內、在他面前凌辱王后。這意味著王認為哈曼試圖強暴她。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17007008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 7:8",
          "end_ref": "17007008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 7:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571695,
    "reference_id": 123330,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 7:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17007009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>王說要把哈曼掛在哪裡？</strong></p><p>王說要把哈曼掛在哈曼為末底改做的五丈高的木架上，正立在哈曼的家裏。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17007009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 7:9",
          "end_ref": "17007009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 7:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571696,
    "reference_id": 123331,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 8:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17008001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼末底改開始來到王面前事奉？</strong></p><p>末底改也來到王面前，因為以斯帖已經告訴王，末底改是她的親屬。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17008001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 8:1",
          "end_ref": "17008001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 8:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571697,
    "reference_id": 123332,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 8:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17008002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼末底改負責管理哈曼的家產？</strong></p><p>以斯帖派末底改管理哈曼的家產。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17008002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 8:2",
          "end_ref": "17008002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 8:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571698,
    "reference_id": 123333,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 8:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17008004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>王做了什麼讓以斯帖能夠起來站在他面前？</strong></p><p>王向以斯帖伸出金杖，以斯帖就起來，站在王的面前。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17008004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 8:4",
          "end_ref": "17008004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 8:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571699,
    "reference_id": 123334,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 8:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17008005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>哈曼傳了什麼旨意？</strong></p><p>哈曼設謀傳旨，要殺滅在王各省的猶大人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17008005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 8:5",
          "end_ref": "17008005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 8:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571700,
    "reference_id": 123335,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 8:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17008008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼以斯帖要奉王的名再寫一個諭旨給猶大人？</strong></p><p>以斯帖需要再寫一個諭旨，因為奉王名所寫、用王戒指蓋印的諭旨，人都不能廢除。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17008008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 8:8",
          "end_ref": "17008008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 8:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571701,
    "reference_id": 123336,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 8:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17008009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>王的書記是什麼時候被召來的？</strong></p><p>三月，就是西彎月二十三日，王的書記被召來。</p><p></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17008009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 8:9",
          "end_ref": "17008009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 8:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571702,
    "reference_id": 123337,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 8:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17008011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>諭旨中，王准各省各城的猶大人做什麼事？</strong></p><p>王准各省各城的猶大人，聚集保護性命，剪除殺戮滅絕那要攻擊猶大人的一切仇敵和他們的妻子兒女，奪取他們的財為掠物。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17008011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 8:11",
          "end_ref": "17008011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 8:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571703,
    "reference_id": 123338,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 8:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17008017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼那國有許多人入了猶大籍呢？</strong></p><p>那國的人民，有許多因懼怕猶大人，就入了猶大籍。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17008017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 8:17",
          "end_ref": "17008017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 8:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571704,
    "reference_id": 123339,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 9:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17009002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麽無人能敵擋猶大人？</strong></p><p>無人能敵擋他們，因為各族都懼怕他們。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17009002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 9:2",
          "end_ref": "17009002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 9:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571705,
    "reference_id": 123340,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 9:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17009005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>猶太人對他們的敵人做了什麼事？</strong></p><p>猶大人用刀擊殺一切仇敵，任意殺滅恨他們的人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17009005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 9:5",
          "end_ref": "17009005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 9:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571706,
    "reference_id": 123341,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 9:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17009012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>猶大人殺了誰？</strong></p><p>猶大人在書珊城殺滅了五百人，又殺了哈曼的十個兒子。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17009012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 9:12",
          "end_ref": "17009012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 9:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571707,
    "reference_id": 123342,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 9:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17009013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>哈曼十個兒子的屍首怎麼樣了？</strong></p><p>「將哈曼十個兒子的屍首掛在木架上。」王下令如此行。旨意傳在書珊，人就把哈曼十個兒子的屍首掛起來了。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17009013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 9:13",
          "end_ref": "17009013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 9:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571708,
    "reference_id": 123343,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 9:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17009015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>亞達月十四日，猶大人殺了多少人？</strong></p><p>亞達月十四日，書珊的猶大人又聚集在書珊，殺了三百人。</p><p></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17009015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 9:15",
          "end_ref": "17009015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 9:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571709,
    "reference_id": 123344,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 9:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17009017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>在亞達月十四日，住在王各省其餘的猶大人做了什麼事？</strong></p><p>他們在亞達月的十四日安息，以這日為設筵歡樂的日子。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17009017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 9:17",
          "end_ref": "17009017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 9:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571710,
    "reference_id": 123345,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 9:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17009018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼書珊的猶大人，在亞達月第十五日安息，以這日為設筵歡樂的日子？</strong></p><p>書珊的猶大人在十三日、十四日聚集，然後他們十五日安息，以這日為設筵歡樂的日子。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17009018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 9:18",
          "end_ref": "17009018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 9:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571711,
    "reference_id": 123346,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 9:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17009019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>住無城牆鄉村的猶大人，即那住在城市開放地區的人，在亞達月十四日做了什麼？</strong></p><p>他們以亞達月十四日為設筵歡樂的吉日，彼此餽送禮物。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17009019",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 9:19",
          "end_ref": "17009019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 9:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571712,
    "reference_id": 123347,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 9:20–21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17009020-17009021",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>末底改要求猶大人每隔多久守一次亞達月的十四日和十五日？</strong></p><p>末底改規定猶大人每年都要守亞達月的十四和十五兩日，意思是「年年」。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17009020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 9:20",
          "end_ref": "17009021",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 9:21"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571713,
    "reference_id": 123348,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 9:24",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17009024",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>普珥是什麼意思？</strong></p><p>普珥這個名字的意思是「籤」。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17009024",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 9:24",
          "end_ref": "17009024",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 9:24"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571714,
    "reference_id": 123349,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 9:28",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17009028",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麽猶大人和他們的後裔不可廢掉也不可忘記遵守普珥日？</strong></p><p>因這些日子要在各省各城、家家戶戶、世世代代被紀念並遵守。使這普珥日在猶大人中不可廢掉，在他們後裔中也不可忘記。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17009028",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 9:28",
          "end_ref": "17009028",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 9:28"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571715,
    "reference_id": 123350,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 10:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17010001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>亞哈隨魯王使哪裏的人民進貢？</strong></p><p>亞哈隨魯王使旱地和海島的人民都進貢。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17010001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 10:1",
          "end_ref": "17010001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 10:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571716,
    "reference_id": 123351,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 10:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17010002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>亞哈隨魯王以權柄能力所行的都記載在哪裡？</strong></p><p>他以權柄能力所行的，並他抬舉末底改使他高升的事，豈不都寫在米底亞和波斯王的歷史上嗎？</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17010002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 10:2",
          "end_ref": "17010002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 10:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571717,
    "reference_id": 123352,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 10:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17010003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>猶大人末底改是什麼地位？</strong></p><p>猶大人末底改作亞哈隨魯王的宰相。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "17010003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EST 10:3",
          "end_ref": "17010003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EST 10:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571718,
    "reference_id": 123353,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯帖記 10:3 (#2)",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "17010003",
    "language": "zht",
